{"tid":227518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴僱員工會促下月起加薪一成二","createTime":"2017-05-03T08:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T23:22:39.000Z","uid":4181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7374637e89d0fa2d827c44fe874cf1a2d9bf35a","tid":227518,"uid":4181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"九巴僱員工會促下月起加薪一成二 更新：2017/05/03 14:07<br />\n代表一千名員工的九巴僱員工會要求下月起加薪一成二。 <br />\n<br />\n工會表示，九巴去年盈利超過六億元，增長兩成，應可滿足加薪訴求，要求資方由下月起，除加薪一成二，同時延長所有員工的退休年齡至六十五歲，並要求月薪員工跟日薪員工看齊，於指定日子當值可享有「雙補水」，車長跟文職一樣，每年有十七天有薪勞工假期，另外所有做滿五年的員工，可享有三張直系親屬免費乘車證。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九巴僱員工會成立兩年，有約一千名會員，包括車長、站長和文職等工種，工會指如果資方不積極回應，會發起靜坐及抗議。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/504147/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E4%B8%80%E6%88%90%E4%BA%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F504147%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%258C&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=efae8e05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F504147%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%258C&h=251f778c\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/504147/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%